1
00:01:34,680 --> 00:01:40,900
[Shadow Love]

2
00:01:41,910 --> 00:01:43,970
[Episode 2]

3
00:02:09,360 --> 00:02:13,620
[The Imperial Palace of Taijin]

4
00:02:24,060 --> 00:02:24,860
Your Majesty.

5
00:02:30,560 --> 00:02:31,310
Li Wei,

6
00:02:31,920 --> 00:02:32,870
do you admit your guilt?

7
00:02:32,870 --> 00:02:33,710
Your Majesty,

8
00:02:33,710 --> 00:02:34,430
I do.

9
00:02:35,310 --> 00:02:36,910
You launched a night attack,

10
00:02:37,590 --> 00:02:39,750
yet the Yao Army ambushed us precisely.

11
00:02:39,750 --> 00:02:41,470
Either they were too cunning,

12
00:02:41,470 --> 00:02:43,360
or you're unfit to command.

13
00:02:43,360 --> 00:02:45,360
Or worse, there's a spy in your army.

14
00:02:46,750 --> 00:02:47,470
Besides,

15
00:02:47,870 --> 00:02:49,400
your daughter Li Shuang...

16
00:02:50,430 --> 00:02:51,710
charged in on her own.

17
00:02:51,710 --> 00:02:53,430
If Lucheng had fallen,

18
00:02:53,800 --> 00:02:55,079
even executing you all

19
00:02:55,079 --> 00:02:56,310
wouldn't be enough
to calm the people's rage.

20
00:02:56,310 --> 00:02:57,110
Your Majesty.

21
00:02:57,840 --> 00:03:00,190
I authorized Li Shuang
to lead the troops into battle.

22
00:03:00,190 --> 00:03:01,910
It was a desperate move
in a moment of crisis.

23
00:03:01,910 --> 00:03:03,590
Your Majesty, please reconsider.

24
00:03:03,590 --> 00:03:05,050
A desperate move, you say?

25
00:03:07,000 --> 00:03:08,800
How dare you Li family

26
00:03:08,800 --> 00:03:10,329
gamble with my Taijin land!

27
00:03:11,680 --> 00:03:15,320
[Su Muyang, Crown Prince of Taijin]

28
00:03:12,520 --> 00:03:13,150
Father.

29
00:03:14,430 --> 00:03:16,750
General Li has led
the Changfeng Army for years.

30
00:03:16,750 --> 00:03:18,430
He's brought home countless victories.

31
00:03:18,430 --> 00:03:19,240
Fortunately,

32
00:03:19,320 --> 00:03:20,220
we won this battle

33
00:03:20,220 --> 00:03:21,680
and Lucheng still stands.

34
00:03:22,030 --> 00:03:23,450
Please, Father, don't be angry.

35
00:03:23,450 --> 00:03:27,800
[Su Muli, Prince Li of Taijin]

36
00:03:23,960 --> 00:03:25,750
Five thousand soldiers died in the valley,

37
00:03:25,750 --> 00:03:27,280
and you call that a victory?

38
00:03:27,360 --> 00:03:29,150
Are you defending the Li family

39
00:03:29,400 --> 00:03:31,130
because of your past with them?

40
00:03:34,530 --> 00:03:37,470
[Prime Minister of Taijin, Ji Lan]

41
00:03:37,100 --> 00:03:37,910
Your Majesty,

42
00:03:38,150 --> 00:03:39,400
in my opinion,

43
00:03:39,400 --> 00:03:42,240
the Battle of Lucheng resulted in heavy losses,

44
00:03:42,240 --> 00:03:43,750
but General Li

45
00:03:43,750 --> 00:03:45,710
has long defended Taijin's border

46
00:03:45,710 --> 00:03:45,870
has long defended Taijin's border

47
00:03:45,870 --> 00:03:48,360
with the Changfeng Army.

48
00:03:48,360 --> 00:03:50,360
His service is beyond doubt.

49
00:03:50,360 --> 00:03:52,400
I urge Your Majesty to reconsider.

50
00:03:56,710 --> 00:03:57,430
Enough.

51
00:03:58,430 --> 00:03:59,079
Li Wei,

52
00:03:59,560 --> 00:04:00,960
for your past service,

53
00:04:01,120 --> 00:04:02,520
I'll let this go, for now.

54
00:04:02,750 --> 00:04:03,870
You have half a month to find

55
00:04:03,870 --> 00:04:04,600
the traitor.

56
00:04:04,680 --> 00:04:05,430
Yes, Your Majesty!

57
00:04:05,430 --> 00:04:07,400
You've fought hard on the front lines.

58
00:04:07,400 --> 00:04:09,079
Rest at home for now.

59
00:04:09,520 --> 00:04:11,400
Let Li Shuang lead the investigation.

60
00:04:11,400 --> 00:04:12,520
If she finds the traitor,

61
00:04:12,520 --> 00:04:13,800
your faults may be redeemed.

62
00:04:13,800 --> 00:04:15,120
If not,

63
00:04:15,430 --> 00:04:16,290
the rest of you,

64
00:04:16,560 --> 00:04:18,620
tell me what punishment he deserves.

65
00:04:22,870 --> 00:04:23,450
Your Majesty,

66
00:04:23,450 --> 00:04:25,110
if we fail to find the traitor,

67
00:04:25,510 --> 00:04:27,440
I'll accept full responsibility.

68
00:04:33,410 --> 00:04:35,290
Just as you predicted, General.

69
00:04:35,770 --> 00:04:36,610
We looked into strange movements

70
00:04:36,610 --> 00:04:38,870
among the soldiers' families,

71
00:04:38,870 --> 00:04:41,390
then we found that
only one fled the capital,

72
00:04:41,510 --> 00:04:42,910
and has now gone missing.

73
00:04:43,800 --> 00:04:45,130
It's the Deputy General

74
00:04:45,190 --> 00:04:46,120
Huo Du's family.

75
00:04:48,300 --> 00:04:50,120
On the day of the Battle of Lucheng,

76
00:04:50,120 --> 00:04:51,430
after planning the surprise attack,

77
00:04:51,430 --> 00:04:52,160
Huo Du

78
00:04:52,360 --> 00:04:53,950
pretended to be sick to avoid the battle,

79
00:04:53,950 --> 00:04:55,950
yet the Yao Army was fully prepared.

80
00:04:56,450 --> 00:04:57,500
These two things

81
00:04:57,860 --> 00:04:59,390
are a bit too coincidental.

82
00:04:59,510 --> 00:05:00,909
We can't wait any longer.

83
00:05:00,909 --> 00:05:02,409
The half-month deadline is approaching.

84
00:05:02,409 --> 00:05:04,140
The sooner we find the traitor,

85
00:05:04,390 --> 00:05:05,920
the safer my father will be.

86
00:05:12,850 --> 00:05:13,580
Stop!

87
00:05:14,850 --> 00:05:15,710
Who goes there?

88
00:05:20,190 --> 00:05:22,680
We have the travel permit.
Let us pass quickly.

89
00:05:22,680 --> 00:05:24,270
You think we'll let you pass
just because you say so?

90
00:05:24,270 --> 00:05:25,610
The checkpoint is on high alert today.

91
00:05:25,610 --> 00:05:27,940
All people must be thoroughly inspected.

92
00:05:29,560 --> 00:05:30,740
Greetings, Your Highness!

93
00:05:30,740 --> 00:05:32,420
We didn't know it was you.

94
00:05:32,580 --> 00:05:33,770
Please forgive us.

95
00:05:33,800 --> 00:05:35,120
Your vigilance

96
00:05:35,610 --> 00:05:36,860
speaks well of your duty.

97
00:05:36,860 --> 00:05:38,520
There's no need to apologize.

98
00:05:38,940 --> 00:05:40,540
May I proceed now?

99
00:05:40,730 --> 00:05:42,390
Safe travels, Your Highness.

100
00:05:55,820 --> 00:05:57,650
To put it nicely,
we call him "Your Highness",

101
00:05:57,650 --> 00:05:58,870
but you know what people really say...

102
00:05:58,870 --> 00:05:59,550
Shut up!

103
00:05:59,830 --> 00:06:01,020
Gossiping about the Crown Prince?

104
00:06:01,020 --> 00:06:02,820
You want to get yourself killed?

105
00:06:03,400 --> 00:06:05,060
Report this to Lord Li immediately.

106
00:06:05,060 --> 00:06:05,700
Yes, sir.

107
00:06:23,480 --> 00:06:24,190
Be careful.

108
00:06:25,190 --> 00:06:26,120
Are you alright?

109
00:06:26,310 --> 00:06:26,830
Hold on.

110
00:06:30,750 --> 00:06:31,480
Muyang,

111
00:06:31,900 --> 00:06:33,160
we're not fugitives.

112
00:06:33,500 --> 00:06:37,350
[Tai Jin Li Ting]

113
00:06:33,750 --> 00:06:36,010
Why did we sneak out
of the city like that?

114
00:06:36,240 --> 00:06:38,190
General Li is still under house arrest,

115
00:06:38,190 --> 00:06:40,390
and His Majesty is wary of the Li family.

116
00:06:40,990 --> 00:06:43,680
If they catch you leaving the capital
without permission,

117
00:06:43,680 --> 00:06:45,140
it will bring you trouble.

118
00:06:45,510 --> 00:06:47,680
That house arrest is awful!

119
00:06:48,390 --> 00:06:50,270
Father watches me all day,

120
00:06:50,470 --> 00:06:52,070
and I can't even slip out for fun.

121
00:06:52,070 --> 00:06:53,040
Ting,

122
00:06:54,090 --> 00:06:54,970
your father

123
00:06:55,000 --> 00:06:56,950
sent you to see Li Shuang in Lucheng,

124
00:06:56,950 --> 00:06:58,800
so you'd stay out of politics.

125
00:06:59,870 --> 00:07:02,000
I've already sent word to your sister.

126
00:07:02,000 --> 00:07:03,750
Stay cautious and keep a low profile.

127
00:07:03,750 --> 00:07:05,350
Don't expose your identity.

128
00:07:05,750 --> 00:07:08,040
The road to Lucheng is long and bumpy,

129
00:07:08,360 --> 00:07:09,730
and Shuang is so fierce.

130
00:07:10,420 --> 00:07:12,550
If Father and you hadn't planned this,

131
00:07:12,680 --> 00:07:14,340
I wouldn't even bother going.

132
00:07:18,650 --> 00:07:19,909
This was your sister's

133
00:07:19,909 --> 00:07:21,640
favorite biography.

134
00:07:21,850 --> 00:07:23,190
Please give it to her for me.

135
00:07:23,190 --> 00:07:24,120
Just tell her...

136
00:07:30,450 --> 00:07:31,110
Never mind.

137
00:07:31,750 --> 00:07:33,080
No need to say anything.

138
00:07:35,430 --> 00:07:36,260
Muyang,

139
00:07:37,120 --> 00:07:38,750
since you miss her so much,

140
00:07:39,360 --> 00:07:40,490
why not come with me?

141
00:07:42,800 --> 00:07:43,630
I'm afraid...

142
00:07:45,370 --> 00:07:47,370
I no longer have the right to see her.

143
00:07:50,440 --> 00:07:51,500
It's getting late,

144
00:07:52,680 --> 00:07:53,750
you should go now.

145
00:07:53,920 --> 00:07:54,800
Stay safe.

146
00:08:29,680 --> 00:08:31,000
I've been here for days

147
00:08:31,480 --> 00:08:32,630
and never heard

148
00:08:32,630 --> 00:08:34,690
birds singing in this military camp.

149
00:09:35,470 --> 00:09:37,030
This is your reward for delivering intel

150
00:09:37,030 --> 00:09:38,840
during the Battle of Lucheng.

151
00:09:39,200 --> 00:09:41,110
If you want a good life,

152
00:09:41,300 --> 00:09:42,630
just keep following orders.

153
00:09:42,630 --> 00:09:43,870
Don't worry,

154
00:09:44,070 --> 00:09:46,220
I have a bigger gift for you.

155
00:09:47,270 --> 00:09:49,270
No wonder Li Shuang was so wary of me.

156
00:09:50,080 --> 00:09:51,390
So there really is

157
00:09:51,910 --> 00:09:53,710
a traitor in the Changfeng Army.

158
00:10:07,580 --> 00:10:08,270
General,

159
00:10:08,720 --> 00:10:09,660
Huo Du is cunning.

160
00:10:09,660 --> 00:10:11,710
I tracked him to the woods,
but lost his trail.

161
00:10:11,710 --> 00:10:13,630
I planned to wait outside his tent,

162
00:10:13,630 --> 00:10:14,690
but unexpectedly,

163
00:10:14,720 --> 00:10:16,650
someone else returned with Huo Du.

164
00:10:16,910 --> 00:10:17,710
Was it Jin'an?

165
00:10:18,770 --> 00:10:21,170
I always knew that boy was suspicious.

166
00:10:21,510 --> 00:10:22,460
I'll drag him in,

167
00:10:22,550 --> 00:10:24,680
and interrogate him along with Huo Du.

168
00:10:46,280 --> 00:10:46,870
Lord Huo,

169
00:10:47,360 --> 00:10:48,820
what brings you here this late?

170
00:10:48,820 --> 00:10:49,460
Nothing.

171
00:10:49,900 --> 00:10:50,530
You may leave now.

172
00:10:50,530 --> 00:10:51,060
Yes, sir.

173
00:11:09,710 --> 00:11:10,440
General,

174
00:11:10,690 --> 00:11:11,950
I request an audience.

175
00:11:12,360 --> 00:11:13,090
Come in.

176
00:11:32,480 --> 00:11:35,280
The other day, when I asked
if you feared I was a spy,

177
00:11:35,390 --> 00:11:36,750
I meant no harm,

178
00:11:36,810 --> 00:11:38,210
but you got so defensive.

179
00:11:38,610 --> 00:11:40,090
So I kept an eye out for you.

180
00:11:40,670 --> 00:11:42,200
You kept an eye out,

181
00:11:42,220 --> 00:11:44,020
or were you in cahoots with them?

182
00:11:44,600 --> 00:11:47,080
Even Mr. Ji, an adult, didn't catch him,

183
00:11:47,420 --> 00:11:49,270
and you, with your tiny arms and legs,

184
00:11:49,270 --> 00:11:50,330
say you managed it?

185
00:11:50,510 --> 00:11:52,510
I've always been better than all of you.

186
00:11:52,510 --> 00:11:54,270
Don't forget you lost to me once.

187
00:11:54,270 --> 00:11:54,870
Remember?

188
00:11:56,790 --> 00:11:59,190
That never happened. Don't talk nonsense.

189
00:12:05,580 --> 00:12:06,860
Why did you do all this?

190
00:12:07,470 --> 00:12:08,830
Because I want you to know

191
00:12:08,830 --> 00:12:10,090
that keeping me around

192
00:12:10,150 --> 00:12:11,350
was the right choice.

193
00:12:14,140 --> 00:12:15,210
You did very well

194
00:12:16,480 --> 00:12:17,720
on this.

195
00:12:18,200 --> 00:12:19,130
Ji Ran, Luo Teng.

196
00:12:20,200 --> 00:12:21,720
Huo Du leaked intel

197
00:12:21,980 --> 00:12:23,560
and colluded with the illegitimate Yao.

198
00:12:23,560 --> 00:12:24,760
Now we have the proof.

199
00:12:25,750 --> 00:12:26,550
Go arrest him.

200
00:12:26,600 --> 00:12:27,400
Yes, General.

201
00:12:29,160 --> 00:12:30,620
All the valuables are gone.

202
00:12:30,620 --> 00:12:31,620
He must have fled.

203
00:12:31,910 --> 00:12:32,840
He won't get far.

204
00:12:32,870 --> 00:12:33,600
Go after him.

205
00:12:33,680 --> 00:12:34,280
Remember,

206
00:12:34,900 --> 00:12:35,600
I want him alive.

207
00:12:35,600 --> 00:12:36,150
Yes, General.

208
00:12:36,150 --> 00:12:37,500
Report!

209
00:12:38,980 --> 00:12:39,510
General.

210
00:12:39,630 --> 00:12:41,800
Young Master was kidnapped by bandits
on his way to our camp.

211
00:12:41,800 --> 00:12:43,030
The bandits sent this jade pendant,

212
00:12:43,030 --> 00:12:45,230
asking you to meet them on the mountain.

213
00:12:48,030 --> 00:12:49,290
Why did Ting come here?

214
00:12:51,290 --> 00:12:51,900
Ji Ran,

215
00:12:51,930 --> 00:12:52,720
take a squad

216
00:12:52,790 --> 00:12:54,160
and follow me to rescue Li Ting.

217
00:12:54,160 --> 00:12:55,620
The rest of you stay at camp,

218
00:12:55,620 --> 00:12:57,140
keep searching for Huo Du!

219
00:12:57,390 --> 00:12:58,990
Make sure to catch him alive.

220
00:12:59,080 --> 00:13:00,030
Yes, General!

221
00:13:02,580 --> 00:13:03,860
I'll go with you.

222
00:13:04,370 --> 00:13:05,300
It's dangerous.

223
00:13:05,840 --> 00:13:07,280
No matter how strong you are,
you're still a kid.

224
00:13:07,280 --> 00:13:08,140
Just stay here.

225
00:13:13,940 --> 00:13:15,340
Since you're my soldier,

226
00:13:15,360 --> 00:13:16,820
you must follow my orders.

227
00:13:16,890 --> 00:13:17,490
Go back.

228
00:13:34,380 --> 00:13:35,380
Brothers.

229
00:13:35,930 --> 00:13:37,270
Here are the last two dishes.

230
00:13:37,270 --> 00:13:38,270
We're all set now!

231
00:13:39,600 --> 00:13:41,070
Come on, try this.

232
00:13:41,070 --> 00:13:41,790
Share some with them.

233
00:13:41,790 --> 00:13:43,240
Alright, thanks, boss!

234
00:13:43,270 --> 00:13:43,790
Eat up.

235
00:13:44,360 --> 00:13:45,360
Dig in, everyone!

236
00:13:45,720 --> 00:13:46,630
Okay, boss!

237
00:13:46,630 --> 00:13:47,320
Brothers!

238
00:13:47,320 --> 00:13:48,240
Boss, sit here, come on.

239
00:13:48,240 --> 00:13:50,270
Here, try this dish.

240
00:13:50,270 --> 00:13:51,080
It's amazing!

241
00:13:51,080 --> 00:13:53,120
Sure, thanks, boss!

242
00:13:53,360 --> 00:13:53,910
Cheers!

243
00:13:53,910 --> 00:13:55,750
Let's drink, brothers.

244
00:13:55,750 --> 00:13:56,410
Bottoms up!

245
00:13:56,790 --> 00:13:58,750
You bandit! Let me go!

246
00:13:58,960 --> 00:14:00,120
Do you know who I am?

247
00:14:00,320 --> 00:14:01,510
Let me go! You...

248
00:14:03,750 --> 00:14:05,870
-Starve me to death!
-It'll be worthless if you're dead.

249
00:14:05,870 --> 00:14:07,200
Try starve me to death if you dare!

250
00:14:07,200 --> 00:14:08,360
Do you know who I am?

251
00:14:08,510 --> 00:14:09,550
Ouyang!

252
00:14:09,550 --> 00:14:10,840
-Bandit!
-You're so good at cooking.

253
00:14:10,840 --> 00:14:11,390
Bandit!

254
00:14:11,390 --> 00:14:11,960
Come on.

255
00:14:12,840 --> 00:14:15,440
If you've got the guts,
just starve me to death!

256
00:14:17,210 --> 00:14:21,060
[Leader of Feiyun Stronghold, Ouyang Jun]

257
00:14:17,480 --> 00:14:18,270
Brothers.

258
00:14:18,840 --> 00:14:20,150
Listen up, all of you.

259
00:14:20,910 --> 00:14:21,790
Tonight,

260
00:14:22,550 --> 00:14:23,840
eat and drink well,

261
00:14:24,120 --> 00:14:25,680
so you'll have the strength to work later.

262
00:14:25,680 --> 00:14:26,480
Understand?

263
00:14:26,550 --> 00:14:27,550
Understood!

264
00:14:28,090 --> 00:14:28,680
Cheers.

265
00:14:28,710 --> 00:14:30,950
-Cheers!
-Drink up!

266
00:14:31,040 --> 00:14:32,440
Come on, fill it up.

267
00:14:32,470 --> 00:14:35,270
General Li has been
guarding the border for years.

268
00:14:35,360 --> 00:14:36,560
She's quite a figure.

269
00:14:36,910 --> 00:14:37,770
Are you sure...

270
00:14:38,130 --> 00:14:39,880
she'd dare come here,
risking her own life?

271
00:14:39,880 --> 00:14:40,710
Don't worry.

272
00:14:41,390 --> 00:14:42,310
That girl

273
00:14:42,330 --> 00:14:44,810
has never been afraid of risking her life.

274
00:14:49,850 --> 00:14:50,490
Shuang!

275
00:14:50,610 --> 00:14:51,270
Don't move.

276
00:14:51,530 --> 00:14:53,890
Not hiding underground like a rat

277
00:14:54,180 --> 00:14:56,240
was the worst decision you ever made.

278
00:14:56,320 --> 00:14:58,920
Well, well,
what a grand entrance, General Li.

279
00:14:59,310 --> 00:14:59,830
Huo Du.

280
00:15:00,760 --> 00:15:02,200
Taijin has treated you well,

281
00:15:02,200 --> 00:15:03,870
why did you betray your country?

282
00:15:03,870 --> 00:15:04,800
Treated me well?

283
00:15:05,030 --> 00:15:06,120
In the Changfeng Army,

284
00:15:06,120 --> 00:15:07,600
to put it nicely,

285
00:15:08,030 --> 00:15:09,820
I'm a Deputy General.

286
00:15:09,870 --> 00:15:11,440
But to put it bluntly,

