Where are you going?

572
00:32:12,770 --> 00:32:13,970
I'm going to kill him!

573
00:32:14,160 --> 00:32:14,960
If it weren't for him,

574
00:32:14,960 --> 00:32:16,240
Father wouldn't be under house arrest,

575
00:32:16,240 --> 00:32:17,160
I wouldn't have been forced to come

576
00:32:17,160 --> 00:32:17,960
to this godforsaken place,

577
00:32:17,960 --> 00:32:19,620
and got kidnapped by bandits.

578
00:32:27,830 --> 00:32:30,590
You just said you wanted him alive, right?

579
00:32:30,920 --> 00:32:32,350
Then I'll go with them

580
00:32:32,400 --> 00:32:34,460
and escort Huo Du back to the capital.

581
00:32:43,640 --> 00:32:44,270
Go ahead.

582
00:32:45,390 --> 00:32:47,030
This journey will be challenging.

583
00:32:47,030 --> 00:32:47,830
There might be

584
00:32:48,000 --> 00:32:49,460
more bandits and outlaws,

585
00:32:49,590 --> 00:32:50,920
or Huo Du's remaining men.

586
00:32:50,920 --> 00:32:52,800
Since you want
to command the Changfeng Army,

587
00:32:52,800 --> 00:32:54,130
this is your best chance

588
00:32:54,650 --> 00:32:55,780
to earn some credit.

589
00:33:00,280 --> 00:33:02,010
Shuang, you think I can't do it?

590
00:33:02,430 --> 00:33:03,630
Do you know why Father

591
00:33:03,830 --> 00:33:05,830
never taught you to lead the troops?

592
00:33:06,830 --> 00:33:08,290
Because you're impulsive

593
00:33:08,310 --> 00:33:09,200
and arrogant.

594
00:33:10,650 --> 00:33:11,680
So in your eyes,

595
00:33:11,680 --> 00:33:13,110
I'm completely useless?

596
00:33:13,720 --> 00:33:14,480
Right,

597
00:33:14,830 --> 00:33:16,000
you're meticulous,

598
00:33:16,060 --> 00:33:17,550
and Father is brave and mighty.

599
00:33:17,550 --> 00:33:18,270
So what?

600
00:33:18,720 --> 00:33:20,400
In the end,
there was still a traitor in the army,

601
00:33:20,400 --> 00:33:21,550
and he still got punished by His Majesty.

602
00:33:21,550 --> 00:33:22,000
You!

603
00:33:22,160 --> 00:33:22,960
If you're that capable,

604
00:33:22,960 --> 00:33:24,050
then go ahead, do it again.

605
00:33:24,050 --> 00:33:25,380
Stab me rght here!

606
00:33:26,550 --> 00:33:27,930
This time, I'm not wearing a chest guard.

607
00:33:27,930 --> 00:33:28,520
Do it!

608
00:33:32,470 --> 00:33:33,120
General.

609
00:33:37,950 --> 00:33:39,150
Why didn't you report

610
00:33:39,510 --> 00:33:40,510
before entering?

611
00:33:40,680 --> 00:33:43,620
I heard you
and the Young Master were arguing.

612
00:33:43,680 --> 00:33:45,810
I was worried, so I came to check on you.

613
00:33:45,860 --> 00:33:47,100
I acted rashly.

614
00:33:47,240 --> 00:33:48,840
Please forgive me, General.

615
00:33:49,640 --> 00:33:50,310
Tonight,

616
00:33:50,750 --> 00:33:52,580
you intercepted key evidence
of Huo Du's treason,

617
00:33:52,580 --> 00:33:53,910
so you deserve a reward.

618
00:33:55,200 --> 00:33:56,240
Thank you, General.

619
00:33:56,240 --> 00:33:57,320
He's just a low-ranking soldier,

620
00:33:57,320 --> 00:33:59,090
and you treat him with kindness.

621
00:33:59,090 --> 00:34:01,590
But when it comes to me,
it's always scolding.

622
00:34:01,590 --> 00:34:02,750
So in your eyes,

623
00:34:03,030 --> 00:34:03,920
am I worse than him?

624
00:34:03,920 --> 00:34:04,720
That's right.

625
00:34:04,950 --> 00:34:06,880
The Changfeng Army
has no place for idlers.

626
00:34:06,880 --> 00:34:07,940
I only value people

627
00:34:08,770 --> 00:34:10,180
with real talent.

628
00:34:18,850 --> 00:34:20,130
He's just a kid.

629
00:34:20,600 --> 00:34:23,060
If he's wrong,
you should teach him a lesson.

630
00:34:23,150 --> 00:34:25,410
Why are you reluctant to discipline him?

631
00:34:26,640 --> 00:34:27,640
You're a kid too.

632
00:34:28,120 --> 00:34:29,070
There are things

633
00:34:29,480 --> 00:34:30,720
you don't understand yet.

634
00:34:30,720 --> 00:34:31,550
Being young

635
00:34:31,570 --> 00:34:33,150
doesn't mean we don't feel things.

636
00:34:33,150 --> 00:34:35,219
If you truly despised him

637
00:34:35,300 --> 00:34:36,489
as you said,

638
00:34:36,520 --> 00:34:39,330
you wouldn't have
risked your life to save him.

639
00:34:39,710 --> 00:34:40,380
I understand this,

640
00:34:40,380 --> 00:34:41,540
and so does he.

641
00:34:41,810 --> 00:34:44,440
It's just that, sometimes,
the closer you are to someone,

642
00:34:44,440 --> 00:34:45,400
it's hard

643
00:34:45,630 --> 00:34:47,090
to say how you really feel.

644
00:34:53,840 --> 00:34:54,480
I see.

645
00:34:55,260 --> 00:34:56,060
You may go now.

646
00:35:04,630 --> 00:35:05,429
What's wrong?

647
00:35:08,960 --> 00:35:09,889
It's burning up.

648
00:35:10,070 --> 00:35:10,760
Help!

649
00:35:10,929 --> 00:35:11,810
Fetch the army physician!

